\*worker: This path is treacherous. Watch your step.
\*bear: Don't worry, I'll keep an eye out for everyone.

\*dwarf: Stay focused, everyone. We can admire the scenery once we find that flower.
\*warlock: Agreed. We don't know what dangers lie ahead.
